lyrics:
[Verse]
Mrs. Sisco, our history teacher so wise
With knowledge that makes our hearts arise
She takes us back through the pages of time
Guiding our curious minds with grace and rhyme

[Chorus]
Oh, Mrs. Sisco, your lessons unfold
Stories of the past, like treasures untold
With passion and wisdom, you ignite our desire
To learn about history, set our hearts on fire
